class_notes:
(Permission of Instructor Required Prior to Enrollment)


This class meets from 11:30 AM to 12:30 PM on the three following dates: Friday, January 21; Friday, February 25; and Friday, March 25.
course_description: A digital portfolio reflection project in which each student curates coursework, experiential learning opportunities, co-curricular experiences, and leadership endeavors and reflects upon the connections among and impact of this academic work.
